{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4ab94dfb61","title":"人民解放军必须进入西藏","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d900c5ded8","index":0,"year":1950,"month":10,"day":11,"articleId":"4ab94dfb61"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wenji6","name":"毛泽东文集第六卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji6.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"6a6aa2e9e3","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"4ab94dfb61","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中国驻印度大使袁仲贤1950年10月10日关于印度对西藏问题的态度给外交部的报告上写的批语。"}],"contents":[{"id":"211d10ac78","type":"title","text":"人民解放军必须进人西藏！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"4ab94dfb61"},{"id":"6a6aa2e9e3","type":"paragraph","text":"外交部：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"4ab94dfb61"},{"id":"314be0c6ab","type":"paragraph","text":"应告责大使：（一）西藏是中国领土，西藏问题是中国内政问题。人民解放军必须进入西藏。首先希望不经战争进入西藏，故要西藏代表团九月来北京谈判，该团故意拖延，至今尚未动身。现人民解放军已向昌都前进，数日内可能占领昌都。如西藏愿意谈判，代表团应速来京。（二）朝鲜问题应照周总理九月三十日演说内容答复之，即中国不能坐视其邻人受侵略而置之不理，扩大战争的责任应由侵略国担负。外交部拟电送阅。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"4ab94dfb61"},{"id":"c563612d88","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"4ab94dfb61"},{"id":"1234f5f122","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"4ab94dfb61"}],"page":{"id":"84c4b34c66","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"4ab94dfb61","start":229,"end":229}},"wenji6":{"comments":[{"id":"801f4eb92c","publica